{"tid":926594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[喜事連連] 民政事務局前副局長許曉暉離世 終年44歲","createTime":"2018-12-03T14:23:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T14:23:47.000Z","uid":224066,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"087f73be78e2e5ff5169d93d12c20c61122ca715","tid":926594,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T14:23:47.000Z","msg":"許曉暉於2008年加入政府，是擴大政治委任制度下首批副局長，她其後過渡至上屆政府，盛傳是政府架構重組後新設文化局局長人選，但因各界對新設文化局反對聲音甚大，最終開局失敗，她原位留任直至去年中離開，出任副局長一職長達9年。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/44UownACg1HKgSNl34U.OQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/45e081aa56ababcbc7de95b4df22d446\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F44UownACg1HKgSNl34U.OQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F45e081aa56ababcbc7de95b4df22d446&h=37a2494b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n及至近年，許曉暉參與不少文化藝術工作，包括今年初獲委任為香港故宮文化博物館有限公司董事局成員。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/zUITCGTjdxZt9oM0B553bA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/398baaa349382374c4a5d6530bc59993\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FzUITCGTjdxZt9oM0B553bA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F398baaa349382374c4a5d6530bc59993&h=b0de7384&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}